<body>
    <h1>20260528 - Batch Non-Prod Team syncup</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"b63a5fed99a5" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsy=
ncup-=F0=9F=94=B71.Objective(ConfirmedDirection)">=F0=9F=94=B7 1. Objective=
 (Confirmed Direction)</h1>
<p local-id=3D"2434ac26f2b8"><strong>DECIDED / ALIGNED</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"5bcd46f6-d747-4dc1-b9d5-172261d99d9a">
<li local-id=3D"608e178d-3576-4c02-a4e5-a847a4dcc101">
<p local-id=3D"76e83d7988f6">Shift from project execution =E2=86=92 <strong=
>BAU service model</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"622eede0-521e-47be-af91-bad89b2056da">
<p local-id=3D"5418be024d99">Standardize and automate:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"13396c11-9b56-44b8-b06e-b3e3ae14fecf">
<li local-id=3D"fd42aac0-4f3a-4586-9d01-6f60cbcf705d">
<p local-id=3D"4955e4904bb6">File transfer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e6261cd9-8bd6-4a3f-8bd9-884306dbee70">
<p local-id=3D"80e270ab37ec">File share</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"48054d98-4387-4b53-aa55-bcd3a89b0f18">
<p local-id=3D"f953c88caaad">Batch job operations</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"3c109028-07fb-42ee-90a7-eaaa11d557ab">
<p local-id=3D"e1eda5b284b5">Transfer <strong>L0 / L1 operational activitie=
s</strong>:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"81fd52c4-3cd5-415c-9067-62b242e2b3df">
<li local-id=3D"8be9072a-b607-46cd-9a42-e8a498f4a40a">
<p local-id=3D"ffbf755a83d9">=E2=9C=85 From: Batch / PS / App support teams=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b9463c5-a783-4788-adaa-e7cd286d86a7">
<p local-id=3D"a2d4a4efcd6f">=E2=9C=85 To: <strong>GOCC (infra + transfer)<=
/strong> and <strong>GBO (batch execution)</strong></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8b594c3db43e">=F0=9F=91=89 Primary outcome:<br>
Free up engineering/testing teams to focus on <strong>higher-value work (au=
tomation, enhancements, new initiatives)</strong></p>
<hr local-id=3D"6f077ef1-886f-4cba-a850-bb2c6883ff57">
<h1 local-id=3D"30d9812cd2fa" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsyncup-=F0=
=9F=94=B72.CurrentState(KeyFindings)">=F0=9F=94=B7 2. Current State (Key Fi=
ndings)</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"fb87e859881c" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsyncup-Bat=
chOperationsModel">Batch Operations Model</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"3fcda816-655b-4769-a9fe-0124f2fd6740">
<li local-id=3D"133777f7-3a1b-4e22-b66f-130e7092143f">
<p local-id=3D"fa4ca2cd70e4">Batch team currently:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4386e12f-62df-4dd2-8254-6913a6449984">
<li local-id=3D"a05c63b6-682c-47c5-961d-5c2c8125e21e">
<p local-id=3D"d9be484cf91f">Handles <strong>non-prod execution, monitoring=
, and fixes</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"19b60c9d-f7dc-4865-a736-7898d6dcc3b9">
<p local-id=3D"50c32abda7fe">Supports Japan business applications</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"b0835b6f-42d9-495c-a98f-1dded2d15297">
<p local-id=3D"ea6db760d734">Jobs are:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"cc3ef9e2-6be5-4355-b98e-a2893f5b590b">
<li local-id=3D"173746e4-d888-4383-a338-58b68d9d2386">
<p local-id=3D"4010c2ba5881"><strong>NOT centrally scheduled</strong></p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"e98999d1-7e11-43b0-b03e-9958f49b3c37">
<p local-id=3D"2e8f9b73d190">Triggered <strong>on-demand by testing teams</=
strong></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"71694d68-be73-465c-9598-edf8abe8298c">
<h2 local-id=3D"5ca772fbbfe2" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsyncup-Exe=
cutionReality">Execution Reality</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"8929720d-f4dc-44a1-aa19-558af6fcc17b">
<li local-id=3D"cc560ebd-313f-4655-8775-9dd4e65763a2">
<p local-id=3D"cc6326b1ec45">Jobs run via CA / scheduler platform</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"def09d66-2ad5-457c-8564-a5679116e131">
<p local-id=3D"092d3e0380c7">Failures:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"859f6b76-5c81-4792-9c3a-af929b43d143">
<li local-id=3D"6b05c5ee-34d9-402c-9c22-6c208863df68">
<p local-id=3D"2c9955df10ce">Typically caused by:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"cdc1b692-794a-40fc-bd56-e76bcfde2431">
<li local-id=3D"1e96aaaa-1d7e-4ff5-b709-2544cb2a8baa">
<p local-id=3D"d778debe7f39">Data issues</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3db9b3f7-9465-48d1-a397-723e7fa89e75">
<p local-id=3D"1601e6e44c29">code mismatches</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b095fd37-5fdb-4a85-b70c-14f2038ef47d">
<p local-id=3D"0ce08fa26681">inactive applications</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e3bcedf-e03b-4da6-9c1a-92ee82accb2d">
<p local-id=3D"542bd1d010a3">Resolution model:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"94b30085-747b-4db9-aedc-8b8b78eba6b4">
<li local-id=3D"4a3f512d-8801-4a7b-a6ba-86dc24e5e064">
<p local-id=3D"d6314bc67d37">Batch team coordinates with developers</p></li=
>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b493bf7d-3e4b-41a6-9db2-00deb3b6c730">
<h2 local-id=3D"7e69a6c14954" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsyncup-Maj=
orVisibilityGap">Major Visibility Gap</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"399711c8-6efd-4fa3-b02d-9a9dfb06155f">
<li local-id=3D"4b1a8516-9e6c-41e0-9d26-06ae9d167043">
<p local-id=3D"107fb4c827c4">No single <strong>source of truth for:</strong=
></p>
<ul local-id=3D"14240b3d-f7d4-4586-893d-a207862ca83f">
<li local-id=3D"b2f5403a-2ed1-4793-8b14-128269983cb9">
<p local-id=3D"3745c09d0f9c">Job inventory</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"89475aea-c086-42ef-b432-3d9c763832cc">
<p local-id=3D"ac508401b11f">Application coverage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0ceb0428-2385-4bb7-80b6-8aa03f2c4b4a">
<p local-id=3D"39400540dc53">Supporting teams</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4601a9ffdd98">=F0=9F=91=89 Multiple teams involved:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4b01f813-e363-4b59-81b5-00681930dde0">
<li local-id=3D"844920e0-f44c-4c9d-8cbc-c6a4a05e1017">
<p local-id=3D"635840cc366d">Engineering</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d0e3d719-ec08-430b-a841-3e1a90a1a606">
<p local-id=3D"7b878114161c">MDM</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e56d67c-6eb1-4b53-ab6d-941672dc9fb8">
<p local-id=3D"8662d02e1d53">Batch support</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e07c778b-5c02-4c3a-9f25-3ad0a057ef2f">
<p local-id=3D"945714509981">Others (unclear scope)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"88420e8d-fb34-4ac9-bd07-2a796403e7c2">
<h1 local-id=3D"0ffb064a95f1" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsyncup-=F0=
=9F=94=B73.AutomationStrategy">=F0=9F=94=B7 3. Automation Strategy</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"85b046eba7c1" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsyncup-Dir=
ection(ALIGNED)">Direction (ALIGNED)</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"3767e735-b6fc-43f5-895a-072e750d0bda">
<li local-id=3D"976bb164-eefb-498a-a9f5-2ac08b238bff">
<p local-id=3D"3b75f76738ae">Target: <strong>Eliminate manual batch executi=
on</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f6f285e9-4e98-49b8-ae13-4335ce263347">
<p local-id=3D"55a6eaf3fa8d">Move all jobs into:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d206e43d-fe3c-4cce-98d7-c3b514b186f2">
<li local-id=3D"2ed13ce5-6866-4341-8070-2e18bd670bba">
<p local-id=3D"dc8f719badb2">=E2=9C=85 <strong>CAWLA platform (standardized=
 scheduler)</strong></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"f49fe773-ab04-4dc4-b632-50c66958f261">
<h2 local-id=3D"8f13bc6a7757" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsyncup-Cur=
rentProgress">Current Progress</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"3e36471c-4643-40c0-a28a-f1a5ba114bd6">
<li local-id=3D"2541f79c-1e57-4704-b4bc-f343b6f52ae1">
<p local-id=3D"43a8f6a08bb6">QA team:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5f4404be-e3ea-40bd-8b81-089987909955">
<li local-id=3D"9baa5602-31fd-4d21-9faf-a1d7a741392f">
<p local-id=3D"4ea7e51700fc">Built automation tools</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5ec36135-dc5d-4aa4-920a-b280bab2915c">
<p local-id=3D"1f70367a941c">Currently in <strong>testing phase</strong></p=
></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e88b5ed-8b9d-4b7f-9ea3-3fafb945f34c">
<p local-id=3D"aca813dbc46a">Next dependency:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e1e0058d-5849-470f-94ce-c614d16f1e9c">
<li local-id=3D"755b8ed6-2166-4ee8-a016-d58e4b9d3993">
<p local-id=3D"a6b8a9a09bf4">Firewall opening =E2=86=92 broader rollout</p>=
</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4dc9051c-972b-421d-b32a-8ed0bb01b093">
<h2 local-id=3D"c076c31af09e" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsyncup-End=
-StateVision">End-State Vision</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"c579f3df-0f49-4cb7-bb24-397260cc377b">
<li local-id=3D"f18ce907-990e-4312-8d8f-cd2b458998c6">
<p local-id=3D"49a93647414c">End users trigger batch processes directly</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"2e2de2ab-6611-47ef-a9e3-522dc75e2619">
<p local-id=3D"7443fc9d2eb5">Batch team involvement minimized</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5b82cae7-2350-4db5-b24d-ef39282c183c">
<p local-id=3D"1ff0919de87c">GOCC + GBO operate standardized workflows</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"075c8365-a622-4a74-9ff4-85820151579f">
<h1 local-id=3D"edc75667c6b8" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsyncup-=F0=
=9F=94=B74.TransitionModel(Emerging)">=F0=9F=94=B7 4. Transition Model (Eme=
rging)</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"bfc55ae1e7ac" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsyncup-Tar=
getOwnership">Target Ownership</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"88=
9adc2c-ac04-4fc1-b40b-533976d2d1e1" class=3D"confluenceTable">
