<hr local-id=3D"10807215-30f3-41b4-bb6e-db770deb949e">
<h2 local-id=3D"3f7f56c4713c" id=3D"id-20260528-BatchNon-ProdTeamsyncup-Sco=
peofTransition">Scope of Transition</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"05894d33-13d7-455b-b856-9b51bce774f7">
<li local-id=3D"feff5ede-6c4d-40c3-926f-18fc335142d6">
<p local-id=3D"2b8c19412462">Focus initially:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ece2b438-49bf-4e67-a320-a9319934df0c">
<li local-id=3D"484a7662-8aa7-4b36-9278-10c8b8030bd2">
<p local-id=3D"23f475624314"><strong>Non-production batch operations</stron=
g></p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"38aa271f-6272-46c6-a7c9-472f9ed3a318">
<p local-id=3D"c7f8d5578ba6">Use as:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8ebb6d5d-9774-4363-a4c4-58cb166ad772">
<li local-id=3D"b7a64a71-152c-4e15-92b0-d4d21ac5318b">
